Package: lyra-usb-gadget
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 kmod,
Description: configure USB gadget on Luckfox Lyra boards
 This package initializes a simple USB gadget configuration on boot,
 suitable for Luckfox Lyra boards. Among other things, it creates a
 network device that can be used to connect to other computers over USB.
